            <title>[SPARK-20025] Driver fail over will not work, if SPARK_LOCAL* env is set.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-20025</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a bare metal system with No DNS setup, spark may be configured with SPARK_LOCAL* for IP and host properties.&lt;br/&gt;
